# HTML Portfolio Project (Final-1)

## 📌 Project Overview
This is my final HTML-only portfolio project. It is a simple personal portfolio website built without CSS to focus on core HTML structure. The project demonstrates how different sections of a portfolio website are created using only HTML.

---

## 📚 What You Will Learn
In this project, you will learn:

- How to create a personal portfolio using HTML only
- How to structure a multi-section webpage
- How to use navigation links within a page
- How to organize content in a professional layout
- Basics of building a portfolio before adding styling

---

## 🧪 Features of This Project
- Home section (Introduction)
- About Me section
- Education details
- Skills section
- Projects showcase section
- Contact information section
- Simple navigation menu using anchor links

